OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSome dry and bright spells
OL,6,Fat first. Otherwise largely cloudy
OL,7,Fwith showers, heavy at times,
OL,8,Fgradually easing later in the day.
OL,9,FWindy at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry and increasingly sunny on Sunday,
OL,13,Fthe odd light shower at first. Dry and
OL,14,Fbright on Monday. Mostly cloudy
OL,15,FTuesday with rain or showers. Becoming
OL,16,Fwarmer.
